comments: Vucevic (CHI) firms up on his left leg and absorbs the body contact from Okoro (CLE) during the pick.
Caruso (CHI) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes one step before releasing his pass.
Love (CLE) turns his body into DeRozan (CHI) and the contact after DeRozan's gather affects his driving shot attempt.
Play is stopped due to a clock malfunction. After the correction, play resumes with Cleveland retaining possession.
LaVine (CHI) and Love (CLE) jostle for position in the post and marginal contact occurs.
Allen (CLE) gets to ball height and tips the ball during the rebounding opportunity and the arm contact with Vucevic (CHI) is incidental.
Mitchell (CLE) initiates arm contact with Caruso (CHI) that affects his layup attempt at the basket.
LeVert (CLE) establishes himself in Caruso's (CHI) path and marginal contact occurs as Caruso moves into the pick.
Allen (CLE) loses control of the ball as he gathers it.
Mitchell (CLE) makes contact with Dosunmu's (CHI) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Dosunmu (CHI) brings his arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Mitchell's (CLE) arm as he attempts to secure the loose ball.
Caruso (CHI) moves alongside Mitchell's (CLE) path and marginal body contact occurs during the drive.
Dosunmu (CHI) extends his arm forward and legally deflects Mitchell's (CLE) pass away from LeVert (CLE).
Okoro (CLE) moves alongside DeRozan's (CHI) path and the contact during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Caurso (CHI) moves towards Osman (CLE) to make a play on the ball and marginal contact occurs.
Dosunmu (CHI) and LeVert (CLE) engage and disengage as the pick is set and the contact is marginal.
Dosunmu (CHI) briefly extends and retracts his hand from Mitchell's (CLE) side and the contact is marginal.
Vucevic (CHI) legally contests LeVert's (CLE) driving floater attempt in the paint.
The shot clock expires as LeVert's (CLE) shot attempt travels toward the basket but does not make contact with the rim. Possession is properly awarded to Chicago.
LeVert (CLE) slides his hand off of DeRozan's (CHI) body during the inbounds and the contact is marginal.
LeVert (CLE) makes contact with DeRozan's (CHI) left arm, which affects the release of his jump shot attempt.
